22#ifndef corefile_h
23#define corefile_h
24
25struct function_map
26{
27 char * function_name;
28 char * file_name;
29 unsigned int is_first:1; /* Is this the first symbol in an object file? */
30};
31
32extern struct function_map * symbol_map;
33extern unsigned int symbol_map_count;
34
35extern bfd * core_bfd; /* BFD for core-file. */
36extern asection * core_text_sect; /* Core text section. */
37extern void * core_text_space; /* Text space of a.out in core. */
38extern int offset_to_code; /* Offset (in bytes) of code from entry
39 address of routine. */
40
41extern void core_init (const char *);
42extern void core_get_text_space (bfd *);
43extern void core_create_function_syms (void);
44extern void core_create_line_syms (void);
45extern void core_create_syms_from (const char *);
